0.12.5
======
- Bug Fixes:
  - Fix typehead in EndoIconView (Expidus #15100)
- Build Updates:
  - Building libendo-1 can now be disabled (Expidus #15138, #15199)
    - Building documentation still requires libendo-1 since some older
      symbols exists only in the GTK+ 2 library
  - Several components were moved around to align with the correct
    library versions:
    - Helpers are now installed in endo-2 paths, and endo-helper-1 has
      been renamed to endo-helper-2 to follow the library version
    - Pixmaps were moved to an unversioned path (pixmaps/endo) since
      they are used by both versions of the library
    - endo-compose-mail has dropped the library version since it
      does not depend on either version of the library
  - The expansion-to-defined flag was re-enabled
- Translation Updates: Albanian, Bulgarian, Danish, Dutch,
  English (United Kingdom), Finnish, Indonesian, Korean, Spanish

